exercises.name: Arm Curl
exercises.description: Strength training of the arms, the arm curl strengthens the upper arm. Mainly the Biceps.

exercises.name: Abdominal Crunch
exercises.description: Strength training of the core, the abdominal crunch strengthens the abdominal muscles. Mainly the Abdominal Rectus.

exercises.name: Shoulder Press
exercises.description: Upper body strength training, the shoulder press strengthens the shoulder muscles. Mainly the Deltoid muscle.

exercises.name: Leg Extension
exercises.description: Strength training of the legs, the leg extension strengthens the muscles of the upper legs. Mainly the quadriceps.

exercises.name: Seated Row
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the seated row strengthens the back muscles. Primarily the Lattissimus Dorsi.

exercises.name: Chest Press
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the chest press strengthens the pectoral muscles. Mainly the Pectoralis major.

exercises.name: Lat Pull Down
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the lat pulldown strengthens the back muscles. Mainly the latissimus dorsi.

exercises.name: Tricep Dips
exercises.description: Strength training of the arms, the triceps dips machine strengthens the upper arms. Mainly the Triceps.

exercises.name: Diverging Lat Pull Down
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the lat pulldown strengthens the back muscles. Mainly the latissimus dorsi.

exercises.name: Back Extension
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the back extension strengthens the back muscles. Mainly the lower back.

exercises.name: Prone Leg Curl
exercises.description: Strength training of the legs, the Leg Curl strengthens the back of the legs. Mainly the hamstrings and glutes.

exercises.name: Chest Fly
exercises.description: Strength training of the upper body, the chest fly strengthens the pectoral muscles. Mainly the Pectoralis major.

exercises.name: Hip Adduction
exercises.description: Strength training of the legs, the adduction machine strengthens the muscles of the inner legs and thigh muscles.

exercises.name: Leg Press
exercises.description: Strength training of the legs, the Leg Press machine strengthens the muscles thigh muscles. Mainly the Quadriceps.

exercises.name: Dip Chin Assist
exercises.description: Strength training of the arms, the Dip Chin Assist machine strengthens the Triceps and back muscles.
